title: Stade Gabèsien (basketball)
text: Stade Gabèsien (basketball) is a <a href="Tunisia">Tunisia</a>n professional <a href="basketball">basketball</a> team located in the city of <a href="Gab%C3%A8s">Gabès</a>. The team competes in the <a href="Championnat%20National%20A">Championnat National A</a>, the top tier national level.
